## What NOT to Build

- No CI/CD pipeline (Railway handles this)
- No staging environment (single environment for personal use)
- No Alembic migrations (create_all on startup is sufficient for MVP)
- No SSL config (Railway handles this automatically)
- No Redis (in-memory job store is sufficient for personal use)

